name: Punch It!
Lore: 'Ever since Lando''s ''little'' maneuver at the Battle of Taanab, his piloting skills had become legendary.',
Text: 'If Han or your Lando is piloting a starfighter which is defending a battle at a system, add one battle destiny (add two if starfighter is Falcon). Also, starfighter is immune to attrition for remainder of turn.',
